name: Kylo The Doge
description: Kylo the Doge is a famous Shiba Inu known for his hilarious squeaks, dramatic reactions, and expressive face. He rose to fame on TikTok, gaining over 4 million followers and 150 million likes with funny videos of him “playing dead,” reacting to “betrayals,” and jumping through hoops. His exaggerated expressions and high-pitched squeals perfectly capture the quirky charm of Shiba Inus, making him a fan favorite. Kylo is also popular on Instagram and YouTube, where he continues to entertain a growing audience with his cartoon-like personality and lovable antics.
